<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="18300000t" end="42600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">可以再说一遍吗</p>
<p begin="73900000t" end="110200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">希望你能参加为学生举办的战斗活动</p>
<p begin="113300000t" end="135600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">在大驾光临的女王陛下面前</p>
<p begin="135600000t" end="162600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">上演一出技惊四座的夺冠剧</p>
<p begin="261500000t" end="275200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">我拒绝</p>
<p begin="437800000t" end="470600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">足以融化孤独的呼声</p>
<p begin="470600000t" end="508900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">究竟来自于何人？</p>
<p begin="515000000t" end="559200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">向往着温暖 我出发了。</p>
<p begin="559200000t" end="576600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">再来，再来，再来！</p>
<p begin="581400000t" end="598400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">咏唱 交个朋友</p>
<p begin="598400000t" end="614800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">解除 扑克脸</p>
<p begin="614800000t" end="646190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">平起平坐的坦诚交谈</p>
<p begin="647800000t" end="665400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">打破墙壁吧 用转移魔法</p>
<p begin="665400000t" end="681400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">瞬间便融洽相处</p>
<p begin="681400000t" end="697500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">共鸣之和谐 打破孤独</p>
<p begin="697500000t" end="711200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">精准无比 太完美了吧？</p>
<p begin="711200000t" end="774700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">沉默寡言的挑战者 迈出第一步</p>
<p begin="774700000t" end="828600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">生涩的自己也要抱紧</p>
<p begin="832500000t" end="866600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">一起开始尝试！就是现在 尝试！</p>
<p begin="869900000t" end="908000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">向奇迹发起挑战吧</p>
<p begin="908000000t" end="948300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">将无敌的心情连结到底</p>
<p begin="948300000t" end="965300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">放马过来 放马过来</p>
<p begin="965300000t" end="999100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">鼓足干劲 尝试！发展超乎想像</p>
<p begin="1001600000t" end="1033400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">点燃勇气</p>
<p begin="1033400000t" end="1072900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">即使现在相隔遥远</p>
<p begin="1072900000t" end="1107300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">有朝一日 也必定能相互理解</p>
<p begin="1107300000t" end="1123000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">做我的朋友！！！</p>
<p begin="1123000000t" end="1176800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">哔哩哔哩译制<br />Translated by bilibili</p>
<p begin="1203400000t" end="1218100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">你也知道</p>
<p begin="1221100000t" end="1243000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">我们学园是国家机关</p>
<p begin="1243000000t" end="1268800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">为了申请增加预算</p>
<p begin="1268800000t" end="1299300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">战斗活动是千载难逢的机会</p>
<p begin="1299300000t" end="1332400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">您是想把我当成赚钱工具吗</p>
<p begin="1336300000t" end="1346600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">没没没</p>
<p begin="1346600000t" end="1394100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">我是为了学园的未来和学生啊</p>
<p begin="1394100000t" end="1426700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">亚德同学 算我求你了 拜托了</p>
<p begin="1477500000t" end="1498200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">请抬起头来 校长</p>
<p begin="1510200000t" end="1558300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">我认为魔法应该用来帮助有困难的人</p>
<p begin="1563900000t" end="1590600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">就算是为了预算 也不该用来表演…</p>
<p begin="1590600000t" end="1612400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">意思是这违背了你的美学吗</p>
<p begin="1623200000t" end="1671600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">我的某个笨弟弟以前也说过同样的话</p>
<p begin="1677300000t" end="1702600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">只可惜他擅自转生了</p>
<p begin="1705800000t" end="1750400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">没机会找他问清楚美学的意义何在了</p>
<p begin="1753300000t" end="1768100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">笨弟弟…</p>
<p begin="1771000000t" end="1792200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">只不过 我们没有血缘关系</p>
<p begin="1792200000t" end="1810200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">因为我跟他都是孤儿</p>
<p begin="1829200000t" end="1838400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">校长</p>
<p begin="1843300000t" end="1870300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">可以给我一点时间考虑吗</p>
<p begin="1875100000t" end="1910900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">当然可以 期待你的好消息</p>
<p begin="1913900000t" end="1948700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">我倒要好好看看你究竟是谁</p>
<p begin="1953800000t" end="1972900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">大魔导师的儿子</p>
<p begin="2002300000t" end="2017600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">这该如何是好</p>
<p begin="2022600000t" end="2051800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">如果拒绝 学费减免就会被取消</p>
<p begin="2055100000t" end="2078600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">最坏的情况下我可能会被开除</p>
<p begin="2085000000t" end="2113200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">这样一来 我跟伊莉娜的校园生活</p>
<p begin="2116800000t" end="2129700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">就化为泡影了</p>
<p begin="2133600000t" end="2164700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">可是 在奥利维安眼皮子底下参加战斗活动</p>
<p begin="2168000000t" end="2179600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">没有比这更危险的事了</p>
<p begin="2189700000t" end="2199600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">亚德先生</p>
<p begin="2214200000t" end="2230000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">哦？金妮同学</p>
<p begin="2235400000t" end="2244800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">怎么了</p>
<p begin="2253800000t" end="2283800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">请问 放…放学后你要是没安排</p>
<p begin="2287300000t" end="2302200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">可以跟我约会吗</p>
<p begin="2307400000t" end="2313700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">啊？</p>
<p begin="2321000000t" end="2338100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">约会吗</p>
<p begin="2340900000t" end="2348100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">是的</p>
<p begin="2354100000t" end="2371400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">约会就是那个吗</p>
<p begin="2375000000t" end="2409900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">恋人之间的那种约会吗</p>
<p begin="2419200000t" end="2448700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">可为什么她要找我呢</p>
<p begin="2453600000t" end="2466100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">不不不</p>
<p begin="2468800000t" end="2492200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">你不能误会 亚德·梅特奥尔</p>
<p begin="2492200000t" end="2513800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">也不该想入非非</p>
<p begin="2519500000t" end="2536200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">这种情况下该当即回绝她</p>
<p begin="2542600000t" end="2553700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">可以吗</p>
<p begin="2601100000t" end="2629500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">好吧 放学后我陪你</p>
<p begin="2629500000t" end="2656100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">太好了 跟亚德先生约会</p>
<p begin="2656100000t" end="2679300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">我也有一个请求</p>
<p begin="2692400000t" end="2707700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">不要叫我亚德「先生」</p>
<p begin="2707700000t" end="2731200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">可以直接叫我「亚德」吗？</p>
<p begin="2734600000t" end="2756300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">毕竟我们都是同学了</p>
<p begin="2759600000t" end="2779100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">怎么可以直呼你的名字</p>
<p begin="2779100000t" end="2808500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">那么 至少改成「同学」吧</p>
<p begin="2808500000t" end="2833000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">同学…亚德「同学」？</p>
<p begin="2836100000t" end="2855700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">是的 我觉得还是这样叫比较好</p>
<p begin="2874300000t" end="2908100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">亚德同学 我很期待跟你约会</p>
<p begin="2910900000t" end="2919000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">我才是…</p>
<p begin="2919000000t" end="2936000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">给我等一下</p>
<p begin="2939900000t" end="2953200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">伊莉娜小姐</p>
<p begin="2953200000t" end="2980400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">我…我也要去 我也想去约会</p>
<p begin="3018900000t" end="3037900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">好 完全没问题啊</p>
<p begin="3046400000t" end="3071000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">真…真的可以吗？可你不是…</p>
<p begin="3076100000t" end="3110700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">我又没想独占亚德同学</p>
<p begin="3122600000t" end="3164800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">我反而认为亚德同学应该开后宫</p>
<p begin="3191000000t" end="3208100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">「后宫」是什么啊</p>
<p begin="3215400000t" end="3229700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">你不知道吗</p>
<p begin="3235900000t" end="3255800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">后宫就是…</p>
<p begin="3301400000t" end="3333100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">不…不行 不行不行 绝对不行</p>
<p begin="3333100000t" end="3362900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">我绝不认同什么后宫</p>
<p begin="3374400000t" end="3385000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">为什么啊</p>
<p begin="3388100000t" end="3422100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">如果亚德同学身边有众多女孩</p>
<p begin="3422100000t" end="3441100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">我觉得挺帅的啊</p>
<p begin="3441100000t" end="3456200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">说不行就不行</p>
<p begin="3547500000t" end="3567200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">亚德同学 伊莉娜小姐</p>
<p begin="3595400000t" end="3609100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">金妮 你好可爱啊</p>
<p begin="3613900000t" end="3631100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">你也很可爱哦</p>
<p begin="3655100000t" end="3700800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">不过 看着两位美少女嬉戏</p>
<p begin="3703700000t" end="3720600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">心灵好像得到了净化一般</p>
<p begin="3724300000t" end="3756300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">亚德同学 我这身怎么样啊</p>
<p begin="3759800000t" end="3779500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">为了约会 我努力打扮了一下</p>
<p begin="3790800000t" end="3812900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">真是打扮得恰到好处</p>
<p begin="3816400000t" end="3841900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">亚德 也夸夸我啊</p>
<p begin="3846600000t" end="3865900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">你也很美</p>
<p begin="3865900000t" end="3875200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">是吧</p>
<p begin="3878800000t" end="3919400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">因为是第一次约会 我选择了传统约会项目戏剧鉴赏</p>
<p begin="3922000000t" end="3943500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">哦？是什么故事啊</p>
<p begin="3951000000t" end="3970500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">我乃全能之王</p>
<p begin="3982900000t" end="3994700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">巴尔巴托斯</p>
<p begin="4011000000t" end="4033000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">我要把邪神赶尽杀绝</p>
<p begin="4043700000t" end="4079500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">竟然要鉴赏自己的一生</p>
<p begin="4172100000t" end="4243200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">看样子金妮下意识封印住的魅魔天赋 慢慢发挥出来了</p>
<p begin="4248400000t" end="4265400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">无论男女老少</p>
<p begin="4265400000t" end="4293700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">都会拜倒在她的魅力之下</p>
<p begin="4297100000t" end="4318200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">这能力和天赋也太高了</p>
<p begin="4327700000t" end="4350800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">就连我…都有点…</p>
<p begin="4404000000t" end="4416600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">不行 不行</p>
<p begin="4419600000t" end="4446700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">我怎么能抱有邪念呢</p>
<p begin="4452300000t" end="4486400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">你过于独断专行了 巴尔巴托斯</p>
<p begin="4493800000t" end="4521900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">多仰仗我一下吧</p>
<p begin="4529200000t" end="4544000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">对不起 莉迪娅</p>
<p begin="4567600000t" end="4598400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">我很担心你 巴尔巴托斯</p>
<p begin="4608800000t" end="4627700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">等等等…等下</p>
<p begin="4627700000t" end="4656600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">这真是魔王巴尔巴托斯的戏吗</p>
<p begin="4659900000t" end="4689000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">我在看谁的鬼故事啊</p>
<p begin="4699000000t" end="4710100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">巴尔巴托斯</p>
<p begin="4722600000t" end="4747700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">我永远在你身边</p>
<p begin="4753100000t" end="4767500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">谢谢 莉迪娅</p>
<p begin="4774100000t" end="4800800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">只要跟你在一起 破碎的心就能获得慰藉</p>
<p begin="4804800000t" end="4843700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">不对 绝对一定根本不对</p>
<p begin="4847800000t" end="4861400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">要说莉迪娅…</p>
<p begin="4911500000t" end="4925500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">喂 等等 莉迪娅</p>
<p begin="4928400000t" end="4954400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">现在冲上去 战术就白准备了</p>
<p begin="4957700000t" end="4970000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">少他妈啰唆</p>
<p begin="4970000000t" end="4985400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">给我冲 小的们</p>
<p begin="5006100000t" end="5029100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">打赢就行了 打赢</p>
<p begin="5036200000t" end="5055000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">她可是这种人啊</p>
<p begin="5079500000t" end="5096200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">花开了</p>
<p begin="5107600000t" end="5124790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">还花呢</p>
<p begin="5145300000t" end="5156300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">累死了</p>
<p begin="5167700000t" end="5215890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">吐槽演出和回忆杀搞得我筋疲力尽</p>
<p begin="5218590000t" end="5240500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">真是太好看了</p>
<p begin="5240500000t" end="5271600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">魔王巴尔巴托斯陛下就是帅</p>
<p begin="5271600000t" end="5288900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">啊…嗯…</p>
<p begin="5293300000t" end="5314900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">不过 如果是一个人看</p>
<p begin="5314900000t" end="5337000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">应该不会这么开心</p>
<p begin="5343300000t" end="5362000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">都是因为有亚德同学的陪伴</p>
<p begin="5413000000t" end="5454300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">我说 是时候去吃饭了吧</p>
<p begin="5454300000t" end="5490100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">我知道家不错的店 我来带路</p>
<p begin="5517900000t" end="5541500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157">金妮小姐 这 这里是…</p>
<p begin="5541500000t" end="5562800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">喂 亚德 我看不见了</p>
<p begin="5562800000t" end="5591800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">前面有家不为人知的名店</p>
<p begin="5596900000t" end="5608100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">真是的</p>
<p begin="5611100000t" end="5635800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">事已至此 只能跟着去了</p>
<p begin="5682200000t" end="5700800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">那女人也太顽强了</p>
<p begin="5704700000t" end="5762600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">- 好歹也是被人奉为女神圣使的人<br />- 亚德？</p>
<p begin="5768000000t" end="5798300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">不过 她就算贵为女王也终究是人类</p>
<p begin="5802100000t" end="5824400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">- 气数快到头了吧<br />- 亚德？</p>
<p begin="5830700000t" end="5860600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">我们要趁现在把女王控制住</p>
<p begin="5889300000t" end="5905100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">怎么了 亚德同…</p>
<p begin="5905100000t" end="5911400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">嘘</p>
<p begin="5937900000t" end="5958800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">那个魔法阵一旦完成</p>
<p begin="5962400000t" end="5980500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">即便是女王 也不可能毫发无损</p>
<p begin="5988800000t" end="5998600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">该走了</p>
<p begin="6036900000t" end="6063600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">我想去跟踪他们</p>
<p begin="6067600000t" end="6092500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">很抱歉 要中断约会了</p>
<p begin="6097300000t" end="6103600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">你们就…</p>
<p begin="6103600000t" end="6121800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">我也要陪你一起去</p>
<p begin="6124900000t" end="6153100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">危险正在逼近女王 怎么能坐视不理</p>
<p begin="6156700000t" end="6166400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">我也一样</p>
<p begin="6169900000t" end="6202300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">我跟以前不同了 以我现在的实力</p>
<p begin="6202300000t" end="6222100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">应该能帮上忙的</p>
<p begin="6263400000t" end="6273600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">好吧</p>
<p begin="6278800000t" end="6316600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">我可以保证你们最起码的人身安全</p>
<p begin="6479800000t" end="6510300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">越来越可疑了啊</p>
<p begin="6632000000t" end="6645900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">魔法阵？</p>
<p begin="6649900000t" end="6662100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">这也太大了</p>
<p begin="6677500000t" end="6694700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">啊 我懂了</p>
<p begin="6698600000t" end="6713400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">是这么回事啊</p>
<p begin="6720200000t" end="6733400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">「这么回事」？</p>
<p begin="6737000000t" end="6750300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">看来我们…</p>
<p begin="6750300000t" end="6773300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">不许动 否则就杀了你们</p>
<p begin="6786700000t" end="6798800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">果然是陷阱啊</p>
<p begin="6812700000t" end="6833900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">彻底上钩了啊</p>
<p begin="6837700000t" end="6856200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">别轻举妄动哦</p>
<p begin="6860800000t" end="6895800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">你们的生杀大权在我们手上</p>
<p begin="6925700000t" end="6951100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">胆子真不小啊</p>
<p begin="6955000000t" end="6974800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195">你们以为能逃掉不成</p>
<p begin="6983400000t" end="6998400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196">这个嘛</p>
<p begin="6998400000t" end="7040300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">我觉得你们无意杀死我们</p>
<p begin="7046200000t" end="7063700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">如果你们想杀死我们</p>
<p begin="7066700000t" end="7095500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">你们大可偷袭 有的是办法</p>
<p begin="7104900000t" end="7147800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200">说到底 你们用明显不对劲的对话引诱我们</p>
<p begin="7150900000t" end="7178200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201">而且事先构建好了魔法阵</p>
<p begin="7182200000t" end="7202700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202">从那一刻起我就知道了</p>
<p begin="7207300000t" end="7241400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203">你们没打算杀我们 而是想绑架活口</p>
<p begin="7241400000t" end="7257900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204">你们的企图太明显了</p>
<p begin="7264100000t" end="7279300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205">另外 还有一点</p>
<p begin="7322900000t" end="7332800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206">亚德</p>
<p begin="7332800000t" end="7343700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207">亚德同学</p>
<p begin="7389600000t" end="7421600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208">你只说对了一半</p>
<p begin="7421600000t" end="7466300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209">除了目标 没必要留活口</p>
<p begin="7511000000t" end="7529200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210">你怎么还没死</p>
<p begin="7536600000t" end="7585400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211">你们准备的计谋 对我毫无威胁</p>
<p begin="7659800000t" end="7673700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212">怎…怎么可能</p>
<p begin="7679200000t" end="7698000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">到底是怎么回事</p>
<p begin="7701900000t" end="7716800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">这家伙是什么人啊</p>
<p begin="7720400000t" end="7734600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">身体着火了都没事</p>
<p begin="7737900000t" end="7746700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216">这不可能</p>
<p begin="7746700000t" end="7758700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217">别慌</p>
<p begin="7762100000t" end="7791800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218">对手只有三个人 我们人数还是占优的</p>
<p begin="7801300000t" end="7820100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219">处理你们这种杂兵</p>
<p begin="7823000000t" end="7845900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220">我可不想花太多时间</p>
<p begin="7854400000t" end="7877300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221">毕竟我们还在约会呢</p>
<p begin="7898200000t" end="7905600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222">好了</p>
<p begin="8095200000t" end="8119100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223">我特地没有动你</p>
<p begin="8124300000t" end="8153700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224">只要你坦白埋伏我们的理由</p>
<p begin="8160800000t" end="8186800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225">我倒是可以不对你动粗</p>
<p begin="8186800000t" end="8202500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226">你这怪物</p>
<p begin="8202500000t" end="8221700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227">我是不会让你如意的</p>
<p begin="8300900000t" end="8309500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228">魔族？</p>
<p begin="8325000000t" end="8352200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229">好吧 是这么回事啊</p>
<p begin="8375400000t" end="8397600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230">「雷电爆发」</p>
<p begin="8461300000t" end="8476100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231">他…逃走了吗</p>
<p begin="8479600000t" end="8501800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232">好像是的</p>
<p begin="8507800000t" end="8534900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233">二位 我要去追他</p>
<p begin="8552400000t" end="8580400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234">可是 那家伙能飞哦</p>
<p begin="8580400000t" end="8613800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235">等我们返回井盖 回到地面的时候</p>
<p begin="8613800000t" end="8634000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236">他早就飞没影了哦</p>
<p begin="8642100000t" end="8666500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237">为什么要原路返回呢</p>
<p begin="8671700000t" end="8708300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238">他飞我也飞就行了</p>
<p begin="8756000000t" end="8776100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239">人类原来是能飞的吗</p>
<p begin="8780100000t" end="8814900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240">还请记好了 我是能飞的</p>
<p begin="8942000000t" end="8950000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241">怎么了</p>
<p begin="9039700000t" end="9052800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242">来人啊 救救我女儿</p>
<p begin="9079500000t" end="9096900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243">喂 那该不会是…</p>
<p begin="9100000000t" end="9130900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244">快…快跑 魔族来了</p>
<p begin="9140100000t" end="9175200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245">不妙啊 这样下去恐慌会扩散开的</p>
<p begin="9180600000t" end="9196100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246">要平息这场恐慌…</p>
<p begin="9216500000t" end="9233200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247">听好了 各位民众</p>
<p begin="9248300000t" end="9269400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248">我名叫亚德·梅特奥尔</p>
<p begin="9274800000t" end="9312000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249">是大魔导师杰克·梅特奥尔的儿子</p>
<p begin="9315300000t" end="9343400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250">梅特奥尔？那个大魔导师的儿子？</p>
<p begin="9349400000t" end="9363000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251">那边的魔族</p>
<p begin="9363000000t" end="9390400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252">已被我逼得走投无路 形同死人了</p>
<p begin="9395700000t" end="9434800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253">接下来 这个威胁诸位生活的歹徒</p>
<p begin="9434800000t" end="9447900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254">将被我制裁</p>
<p begin="9447900000t" end="9472600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255">制裁？我手上可有人质…</p>
<p begin="9472600000t" end="9482900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256">人质？</p>
<p begin="9485900000t" end="9508700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257">你所谓的人质在哪呢</p>
<p begin="9531700000t" end="9565400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258">你什么时候产生了手上有人质的错觉？</p>
<p begin="9570300000t" end="9589500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259">你干了…什么…</p>
<p begin="9595000000t" end="9615000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260">用了一点幻觉魔法</p>
<p begin="9622100000t" end="9656400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261">话说回来 魔族也真是堕落了</p>
<p begin="9663000000t" end="9678700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262">你是什么人</p>
<p begin="9700400000t" end="9718000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263">只是个路过的…</p>
<p begin="9721800000t" end="9732900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264">村民罢了</p>
<p begin="9748600000t" end="9791500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265">世上怎么可能有你这种村民啊</p>
<p begin="9795000000t" end="9829900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266">你好像不明白 我就教教你好了</p>
<p begin="9848900000t" end="9873100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267">你可没法逃出我的掌心</p>
<p begin="9890300000t" end="9906800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268">巴比伦之光</p>
<p begin="10038400000t" end="10050000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269">我看看…</p>
<p begin="10053000000t" end="10081200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270">那个…孩子得您相救</p>
<p begin="10086700000t" end="10100800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271">真是万分感谢</p>
<p begin="10104900000t" end="10131400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272">哪里 我只是做了我该做的事</p>
<p begin="10157300000t" end="10187200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273">刚才那招 虽然没见过 不过好像很厉害哦</p>
<p begin="10187200000t" end="10202500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274">我见过的</p>
<p begin="10202500000t" end="10221900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275">那是大魔导师的魔法</p>
<p begin="10221900000t" end="10245600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276">那是最强的特级魔法啊</p>
<p begin="10245600000t" end="10267000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277">感激不尽 感激不尽</p>
<p begin="10267000000t" end="10279500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278">大魔导师</p>
<p begin="10279500000t" end="10294600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279">把他举起来</p>
<p begin="10294600000t" end="10301900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280">等…</p>
<p begin="10401000000t" end="10420900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281">发…发生什么事了呢</p>
<p begin="10447600000t" end="10461100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282">此事过后</p>
<p begin="10463990000t" end="10494800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283">我得以谒见女王陛下</p>
<p begin="10507000000t" end="10532600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284">我本想避免出风头的</p>
<p begin="10569800000t" end="10598800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285">抬起头来 亚德·梅特奥尔</p>
<p begin="10622500000t" end="10672100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286">贵为女王 气质和格调果然非比寻常</p>
<p begin="10687400000t" end="10698900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287">喂 平民</p>
<p begin="10704100000t" end="10746300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288">就凭你的身份 岂可直视高贵的陛下</p>
<p begin="10746300000t" end="10757900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289">没事 没事</p>
<p begin="10773300000t" end="10800400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290">为朕的美貌所吸引 看得入迷</p>
<p begin="10805000000t" end="10834100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291">这是生物必然遵循的自然法则</p>
<p begin="10842800000t" end="10876000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292">我想想 究竟该用怎样的态度应对呢</p>
<p begin="10882300000t" end="10902300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293">最好能避开正题</p>
<p begin="10905700000t" end="10945200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294">趁乱退出战斗活动并争取到预算</p>
<p begin="10952000000t" end="10967600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295">小罗 好久不见</p>
<p begin="10994100000t" end="11016100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296">真…真是太放肆了</p>
<p begin="11016100000t" end="11027700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297">简直不堪入目</p>
<p begin="11031000000t" end="11060300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298">干嘛啊 我跟小罗可是朋友</p>
<p begin="11064900000t" end="11091400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299">才不会毫无意义地低头呢</p>
<p begin="11095800000t" end="11113500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300">你还是老样子啊</p>
<p begin="11116800000t" end="11139000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301">这样才是真正的伊莉娜</p>
<p begin="11144200000t" end="11162200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302">伊莉娜是朕的朋友</p>
<p begin="11162200000t" end="11196300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303">所以怎样冒犯和放肆都没关系</p>
<p begin="11217100000t" end="11246500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304">朕绝不允许任何人责怪她</p>
<p begin="11283300000t" end="11310200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305">好了 今天找你们来</p>
<p begin="11310200000t" end="11328400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306">是为了赏赐一事</p>
<p begin="11339100000t" end="11350600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307">在这种情况下</p>
<p begin="11354400000t" end="11382400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308">平民该怎样应对女王呢</p>
<p begin="11388900000t" end="11420600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309">我只以魔王的身份召见过别国的国王</p>
<p begin="11425000000t" end="11454400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310">以平民的身份谒见国王还是第一次</p>
<p begin="11463500000t" end="11490200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311">你的功绩值得称赞</p>
<p begin="11493300000t" end="11502000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312">是</p>
<p begin="11502000000t" end="11523300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313">大魔导师的儿子果然非同凡响</p>
<p begin="11523300000t" end="11531500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314">是</p>
<p begin="11531500000t" end="11570900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315">朕看中你了 所以要赏赐你</p>
<p begin="11570900000t" end="11579100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316">是</p>
<p begin="11579100000t" end="11603400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317">你来当我的丈夫吧</p>
<p begin="11606500000t" end="11612800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318">是</p>
<p begin="11624900000t" end="11637100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319">啊？</p>
<p begin="11640500000t" end="11671400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320">要朕说得更直白点吗</p>
<p begin="11677700000t" end="11693900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321">亚德·梅特奥尔</p>
<p begin="11693900000t" end="11728300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322">你想不想让我怀孕啊</p>
<p begin="11728300000t" end="11745600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323">陛…陛下您疯了吗</p>
<p begin="11749200000t" end="11760800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle324">不行</p>
<p begin="11760800000t" end="11784800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle325">不行不行 亚德可是亚德啊</p>
<p begin="11784800000t" end="11818400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle326">那样一来 女王也要加入后宫了</p>
<p begin="11843000000t" end="11877600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle327">算了 这事就当是玩笑好了</p>
<p begin="11882000000t" end="11896100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle328">来谈谈赏赐</p>
<p begin="11901100000t" end="11934200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle329">朕将你晋升为五边级魔导师</p>
<p begin="11934200000t" end="11948700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle330">五…五边级？</p>
<p begin="11948700000t" end="11967800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle331">竟然将平民升为五边级？</p>
<p begin="11967800000t" end="11981400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle332">三思啊 陛下</p>
<p begin="11989000000t" end="11997800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle333">不妙</p>
<p begin="12014800000t" end="12028600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle334">恕在下冒昧 陛下</p>
<p begin="12043100000t" end="12063500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle335">还望陛下开恩</p>
<p begin="12069800000t" end="12115000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle336">可否满足在下一个小小的愿望 以作赏赐</p>
<p begin="12119100000t" end="12130800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle337">但说无妨</p>
<p begin="12134300000t" end="12186500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle338">恳请陛下为拉维尔国立魔法学园增拨国家预算</p>
<p begin="12186500000t" end="12211000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle339">什么啊 这点小事就可以了吗</p>
<p begin="12215700000t" end="12242300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle340">可这对你有什么好处呢</p>
<p begin="12242300000t" end="12279100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle341">戈尔德伯爵平日对在下关照有加</p>
<p begin="12279100000t" end="12293000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle342">在下想报答他</p>
<p begin="12309700000t" end="12342100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle343">比起满足私欲 竟然优先报恩</p>
<p begin="12345300000t" end="12370100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle344">真是又谦逊又仁慈</p>
<p begin="12374300000t" end="12393300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle345">朕越来越欣赏你了</p>
<p begin="12398000000t" end="12424700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle346">五边级地位和增拨预算</p>
<p begin="12424700000t" end="12442000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle347">都赏你了</p>
<p begin="12457000000t" end="12470300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle348">使不得 陛下</p>
<p begin="12502400000t" end="12515900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle349">好吧 好吧</p>
<p begin="12515900000t" end="12535600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle350">那么加上条件怎样</p>
<p begin="12540300000t" end="12577100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle351">赐给亚德和伊莉娜五边级地位</p>
<p begin="12580700000t" end="12591500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle352">作为交换</p>
<p begin="12591500000t" end="12643800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle353">你们必须加入直属女王的特殊兵团「女王之影」</p>
<p begin="12646700000t" end="12657400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle354">可是 陛下</p>
<p begin="12660500000t" end="12690100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle355">再将奥尔海德的女儿升为五边级就说不过去了</p>
<p begin="12693600000t" end="12708500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle356">没关系</p>
<p begin="12708500000t" end="12747500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle357">反正伊莉娜早晚也能到达这个境界</p>
<p begin="12751700000t" end="12769400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle358">谢谢你 小罗</p>
<p begin="12769400000t" end="12791700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle359">顺便再赏赐下金妮吧</p>
<p begin="12800000000t" end="12812100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle360">也是…</p>
<p begin="12819600000t" end="12845900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle361">就将你升为三角级魔导师吧 怎样</p>
<p begin="12858000000t" end="12877900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle362">谢…谢谢陛下</p>
<p begin="12889500000t" end="12928100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle363">奇怪 为什么…会变成这样</p>
<p begin="12967600000t" end="13000600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle364">他好像比我们想像中厉害啊</p>
<p begin="13003900000t" end="13026000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle365">大魔导师的儿子</p>
<p begin="13026000000t" end="13051400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle366">已经摸清那家伙的力量了</p>
<p begin="13054700000t" end="13082800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle367">那平民实力远超常人</p>
<p begin="13086100000t" end="13123800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle368">然而比不上那个怪物</p>
<p begin="13127200000t" end="13152200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle369">那女人值得信任吗</p>
<p begin="13155500000t" end="13175700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle370">这就是杞人忧天了</p>
<p begin="13175700000t" end="13217600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle371">那女人是真心想毁灭这个世界</p>
<p begin="13221400000t" end="13266700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle372">一切都是为了让我们的主人进行正当的统治</p>
<p begin="13266700000t" end="13295100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle373">以及让世界恢复正确的秩序</p>
<p begin="13430900000t" end="13509200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle374">超乎想像的未来正等待你发现</p>
<p begin="13509200000t" end="13573600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle375">打开大门的钥匙就在心中</p>
<p begin="13628300000t" end="13697600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle376">只要伸出你的手</p>
<p begin="13697600000t" end="13744700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle377">连未来都能改变</p>
<p begin="13744700000t" end="13815300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle378">冲动 渴望 重新开始</p>
<p begin="13822300000t" end="13869100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle379">若是转世重生 不要心存畏惧</p>
<p begin="13869100000t" end="13910800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle380">向甜美的过去告别</p>
<p begin="13914800000t" end="13961600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle381">在这日渐昏暗的世界</p>
<p begin="13961600000t" end="13994100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle382">随波逐流所无法掌握的自由</p>
<p begin="13994100000t" end="14047100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle383">去追求它吧</p>
<p begin="14051800000t" end="14083300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle384">舍弃孤独的强大</p>
<p begin="14085400000t" end="14120600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle385">追求相互理解的温暖</p>
<p begin="14120600000t" end="14155000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle386">将找到的那道光</p>
<p begin="14155000000t" end="14192600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle387">轻抱在怀里前行吧</p>
